item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: I do! I recommend the Level Up to 5kyu and 3kyu video series, along with the Attacking Vitamins. The 007 series is an interesting one since it focuses on trick plays, but it looks promising! I will have to say that I will have to rewatch a lot of those videos though. There is just so much information in them! xD
